name: $ROACH
description: $ROACH is an antifragile meme token designed to thrive in chaos and volatility. Inspired by the unstoppable resilience of the cockroach, it runs on a flat 7% tax and a unique 5-tier pressure-response system. As market pressure increases, so do the rewards for holders - punishing panic sellers and incentivizing diamond hands. Whether it’s FUD, rugs, or total market collapse, $ROACH is built to survive and grow stronger. Just hold to earn. When other tokens die, $ROACH scurries on. It’s not just resistant, it’s antifragile by design.
